### Menguji multiple errors 
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/opportunities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}

{
  "name": "Short",
  "amount": 1000,
  "stage": "INVALID_STAGE",
  "closeDate": "invalid-date",
  "description": "This should fail due to multiple validation errors.",
  "leadId": 999,
  "customerId": 999
}

